metadata.name: Let's be friends
metadata.description:
1/1 digital art by Masidoart.
This is the first art from a collection of dragon stories. 
One morning while walking along a familiar route, I heard a strange rustling noise. The tip of the blue tail slid hurriedly behind the monument to the blue tractor. Curiosity overcame my fear, and I peeked around the corner of the monument. The big black eyes stared at me intently and wonderfully.
